To understand how differentially methylated CpGs associated with CHIP might alter cellular function, we identified gene expression changes associated with CHIP-linked CpGs. We analyzed the associations of CHIP-associated CpGs with changes in cis gene expression (expressed gene [eGene] within 100 kB of CpG) in 2115 FHS participants whose DNA methylation data and whole-blood RNA-seq data were available. At P < 1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
